headline: T. Rowe Price Taps Giving And 401(k) Insights For Advisor Loyalty
summary: T. Rowe Price Group (NasdaqGS:TROW) introduced "The Generosity Effect," a new research and advisor resource program focused on charitable giving. The company released its latest Reference Point 401(k) benchmarking report, providing fresh data on retirement plan design and participant behavior.
